com.cmput301.cs.project.activities

Class EditClaimActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • Activity
      • com.cmput301.cs.project.activities.EditClaimActivity

  • public class EditClaimActivity
extends Activity
    The activity that is called when a New Claim is created or when an existing claim is going to be edited.

    Able to add Expenses and Destinations from this screen as well as StartDate and EndDate.

    A claim must be passed via an intent as App.KEY_CLAIM_ID.

    If there is no claim passed it is assumed that the activity is creating a new claim
